---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Your Studio">
  <main>
    <h1>🎨 Welcome to Your Studio</h1>
    
    <div class="card">
      <h2>✨ Your Site is Ready!</h2>
      <p>
        Congratulations! Your Astro-powered studio site has been automatically set up and is ready to use.
        This starter site was created by Studio Builder Desktop and placed in your Documents folder.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>🚀 Get Started</h3>
        <p>
          Your site is located at: <br/>
          <code>~/Documents/studio/</code>
        </p>
        <p>
          To start the development server, open a terminal in that folder and run:
        </p>
        <code>npm install && npm run dev</code>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>📁 File Structure</h3>
        <ul style="text-align: left; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.9rem;">
          <li>📄 src/pages/ - Your website pages</li>
          <li>🧩 src/components/ - Reusable components</li>
          <li>🎨 src/layouts/ - Page layouts</li>
          <li>📦 public/ - Static assets</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>📖 Learn More</h3>
        <p>
          Check out the <a href="https://docs.astro.build" style="color: #87ceeb;">Astro documentation</a> 
          to learn about building amazing websites with Astro.
        </p>
        <p>
          This starter includes everything you need to create a modern, fast website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>🛠 Next Steps</h3>
        <ul style="text-align: left;">
          <li>Customize this page in <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
          <li>Add new pages in the <code>src/pages/</code> directory</li>
          <li>Create components in <code>src/components/</code></li>
          <li>Build and deploy when you're ready!</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>🎯 Built with Studio Builder Desktop</h2>
      <p>
        This site was automatically created and configured for you. No setup required – 
        just start creating! The Studio Builder Desktop app makes it easy to manage 
        your Astro projects and content.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 